I HAVE A PROBLEM.I don’t know how to rest…А few days ago I discovered that the most important feeling that has been accompanying me for a week is fatigue. I stopped to ask myself - what do I feel? And first thing was coming to my mind straight away - I’m so tired. I decided to take day of and when this day came I realised that I absolutely don’t know what to do 😂I was growing up with words of my parents - the best rest is a change of activity. And I believed it. So I just CANNOT TAKE A REST. I feel like I have to do something if I’m not sleeping. And it’s not normal because everything in our world is cyclical. breath - exhale, surf and ebb, day and night. There is a time to work and there’s a time to take a rest. And I’m learning how to rest. I want to ask you also. How are you talking rest?For me I like to cook, watch movies, just sit and meditate…What else? Do you have the problem to rest at all?🤔Or you have problems with start working?😂
